statements: SELECT * FROM affiliate_partnerships;
SELECT partner_name, partnership_start_date, partnership_status FROM affiliate_partnerships;
SELECT partner_name, partner_email FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'active';
SELECT partnership_id, partner_name, partnership_start_date FROM affiliate_partnerships ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT partner_name, COUNT(*) AS partnership_count FROM affiliate_partnerships GROUP BY partner_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT * FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'active';
SELECT partner_name, partner_email, partnership_start_date FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE partnership_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT partner_name, partnership_end_date, partnership_status FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE partnership_end_date < '2022-12-31' ORDER BY partnership_end_date DESC;
SELECT partner_name, partner_email, performance_metrics ->> 'clicks' AS clicks FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE performance_metrics ->> 'clicks' > '100';
SELECT *, partnership_end_date - partnership_start_date AS partnership_duration_days FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'active' AND partnership_duration_days > 30;
SELECT * FROM affiliate_partnerships;
SELECT partnership_id, partner_name, commission_rate FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE commission_rate > 0.05;
SELECT partner_name, start_date, commission_rate FROM affiliate_partnerships ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT partnership_id, click_count, conversion_count FROM performance_metrics WHERE click_count > 100;
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics ORDER BY revenue DESC;
SELECT * FROM affiliate_partnerships
SELECT partnership_id, partner_name, start_date FROM affiliate_partnerships ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT partner_name, commission_rate FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE commission_rate > 0.05
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics WHERE conversion_count > 50 ORDER BY click_count DESC
SELECT partner_name, start_date, revenue FROM affiliate_partnerships JOIN performance_metrics ON affiliate_partnerships.partnership_id = performance_metrics.partnership_id
SELECT * FROM affiliate_partnerships ORDER BY partner_name ASC;
SELECT partner_name, commission_rate FROM affiliate_partnerships WHERE commission_rate > 0.05;
SELECT partnership_id, SUM(revenue) AS total_revenue FROM performance_metrics GROUP BY partnership_id;
SELECT partner_name, clicks, conversions FROM affiliate_partnerships INNER JOIN performance_metrics ON affiliate_partnerships.partnership_id = performance_metrics.partnership_id WHERE revenue > 1000;
SELECT report_id, partnership_id, optimization_description FROM optimization_reports WHERE LENGTH(optimization_description) > 50;
SELECT partnership_id, partner_name, commission_rate FROM affiliate_partnerships;
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics WHERE clicks > 100 AND conversions < 10;
SELECT partnership_id, partner_name, revenue FROM affiliate_partnerships ORDER BY revenue DESC;
SELECT p.partner_name, r.clicks, r.revenue FROM affiliate_partnerships p JOIN performance_metrics r ON p.partnership_id = r.partnership_id;
SELECT p.partner_name, o.optimization_description FROM affiliate_partnerships p LEFT JOIN optimization_reports o ON p.partnership_id = o.partnership_id;
SELECT * FROM affiliates
SELECT affiliate_name, commission_rate FROM affiliates
SELECT sale_id, sale_date, sale_amount FROM sales WHERE sale_amount > 1000
SELECT product_name, product_price FROM products ORDER BY product_price DESC
SELECT affiliate_id, COUNT(*) AS total_sales FROM sales GROUP BY affiliate_id
SELECT * FROM affiliates WHERE affiliate_id = 1;
SELECT affiliate_id, affiliate_name, commission_rate FROM affiliates WHERE commission_rate > 0.05 ORDER BY commission_rate DESC;
SELECT products.product_name, sales.sale_amount FROM products INNER JOIN sales ON products.product_id = sales.product_id WHERE sales.sale_amount > 1000;
SELECT affiliate_name, SUM(revenue) AS total_revenue FROM affiliates INNER JOIN performance_metrics ON affiliates.affiliate_id = performance_metrics.affiliate_id GROUP BY affiliate_name;

SELECT affiliate_name, product_category, AVG(product_price) AS average_price FROM affiliates INNER JOIN sales ON affiliates.affiliate_id = sales.affiliate_id INNER JOIN products ON sales.product_id = products.product_id GROUP BY affiliate_name, product_category ORDER BY average_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM partners;
SELECT partner_name, partner_email FROM partners WHERE partner_id = '1234';
SELECT partner_id, partner_name, partner_email FROM partners WHERE partner_name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT partner_id, partner_name FROM partners ORDER BY partner_name DESC;
SELECT campaign_id, campaign_name FROM campaigns WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' AND end_date < '2022-12-31';

SELECT partner_name, partner_email, campaign_name, conversion_date FROM partners p JOIN conversions c ON p.partner_id = c.partner_id ORDER BY conversion_date ASC;

SELECT reports.report_id, reports.report_date, partners.partner_name, campaigns.campaign_name FROM reports JOIN partners ON reports.partner_id = partners.partner_id JOIN campaigns ON reports.campaign_id = campaigns.campaign_id ORDER BY reports.report_date DESC;
